[How] Update FMT settings for 4:2:0

Reviewed-by: Leo Li <sunpeng.li@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Eric Bernstein <eric.bernstein@amd.com>
Reviewed-by: Rodrigo Siqueira <Rodrigo.Siqueira@amd.com>
